# Depressive Disorders

Educational summaries and practical notes on depressive disorders, aimed at clinicians, residents, and students.

## Purpose
- Outline key clinical features of depressive disorders
- Support differential diagnosis and assessment
- Provide concise, practical educational content

## Planned subtopics
- Core symptoms and diagnostic criteria
- Subtypes and clinical profiles
- Differential diagnosis
- Functional impact and risk assessment
- Overview of treatment approaches
- Patient education and psychoeducation

> Note: Content in this repository is for educational purposes only and does not replace formal clinical training or individualized medical care.
